title: [Empath Guild, Cleaning Cubby]
description: Scrupulously clean tile work covers the floor, set in a diamond pattern and accented with gleaming insets of black and gold.  Atop the sparkling floor, an equally lustrous lacquered chest sits.  The square, gold-handled doors are neatly hinged back to reveal carefully stored cleaning supplies, each neatly tucked into its allotted space.
